About Us

Brands live by their core values and what they add to humanity. Therefore, in the Shoe World, we aim to be the first brand that comes to mind as the most reliable leading shoe retailer that creates value with its price and quality, offers the fashion of the day. This is why we stick to our principles: We are people-centered; We don't just sell shoes, we count the satisfaction of our employees and people as a profit. We are sensitive to society and environment; We respect the good of society and respect the nature. We are reliable; We earn by selling more honestly, not more, and we step on the ground. We are innovative; We follow the world, provide services with the latest technologies and create our own fashion. We are friendly to culture, local elements; We take our strength from these lands and walk arm in arm with local producers.
